of what the food is, if
you say, as of Monday--

00:09:06.340 --> 00:09:07.340 align:middle line:90%
it's always a Monday.

00:09:07.340 --> 00:09:09.510 align:middle line:84%
Everyone's always going
on a diet on a Monday.

00:09:09.510 --> 00:09:13.430 align:middle line:84%
They tend to consume enormous
amounts of food which

00:09:13.430 --> 00:09:15.500 align:middle line:90%
from Friday to the Sunday.

00:09:15.500 --> 00:09:18.925 align:middle line:84%
Sunday, they tend
to go shopping,

00:09:18.925 --> 00:09:21.050 align:middle line:84%
and they put in stuff that
they wouldn't ordinarily

00:09:21.050 --> 00:09:24.797 align:middle line:84%
have ever put in, fruits and
vegetables, as an example.

00:09:24.797 --> 00:09:27.380 align:middle line:84%
Even though, it's funny, because
I've been on a million diets.

00:09:27.380 --> 00:09:29.780 align:middle line:84%
And in the past, when
I went on those diets,

00:09:29.780 --> 00:09:33.490 align:middle line:84%
and I was overweight myself, I
would arrive at the checkout.

00:09:33.490 --> 00:09:37.720 align:middle line:84%
And when I'd get there, on the
day before my diet would begin,

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:39.740 align:middle line:84%
I would have so
much healthy stuff.

00:09:39.740 --> 00:09:41.510 align:middle line:90%
I'd be so proud of my trolley.

00:09:41.510 --> 00:09:43.730 align:middle line:84%
And I'd want the checkout
person to say something.

00:09:43.730 --> 00:09:44.540 align:middle line:90%
Look, this isn't ordinary.

00:09:44.540 --> 00:09:46.250 align:middle line:84%
Look at how much fruit
and veg I've got.

00:09:46.250 --> 00:09:49.190 align:middle line:84%
I would then start on
the Monday morning.

00:09:49.190 --> 00:09:51.820 align:middle line:84%
And I would immediately
start to feel deprived.

00:09:51.820 --> 00:09:55.048 align:middle line:84%
And I think about this, listen,
I could have gone sometimes

00:09:55.048 --> 00:09:57.590 align:middle line:84%
until 2 o'clock in the afternoon
not even thinking about food

00:09:57.590 --> 00:10:01.010 align:middle line:84%
when I wasn't on a diet, without
consuming any food sometimes.

00:10:01.010 --> 00:10:03.260 align:middle line:84%
I'd grab some water,
or sometimes nothing.

00:10:03.260 --> 00:10:04.450 align:middle line:90%
I hadn't thought about it.

00:10:04.450 --> 00:10:10.400 align:middle line:84%
But the very second I told my
brain that I was on a diet,

00:10:10.400 --> 00:10:12.330 align:middle line:90%
I went into the mode of can't.

00:10:12.330 --> 00:10:13.580 align:middle line:90%
What I mean by can't is this--

00:10:13.580 --> 00:10:18.350 align:middle line:84%
C-A-N-T. Constant and
Never-Ending Tantrum.

00:10:18.350 --> 00:10:19.240 align:middle line:90%
It's all it is.

00:10:19.240 --> 00:10:21.930 align:middle line:84%
It's constant and it's never
ending, is the tantrum.

00:10:21.930 --> 00:10:26.180 align:middle line:84%
Now, if you go through, I
want that, but I can't have it

00:10:26.180 --> 00:10:28.760 align:middle line:84%
to I can have it,
but I don't want it,

00:10:28.760 --> 00:10:31.107 align:middle line:84%
there's a massive
paradigm shift.

00:10:31.107 --> 00:10:33.440 align:middle line:84%
For example, look, if I say,
here's a box of chocolates,

00:10:33.440 --> 00:10:34.240 align:middle line:90%
right?

00:10:34.240 --> 00:10:36.800 align:middle line:84%
And let's just say you want
to stop eating chocolates.

00:10:36.800 --> 00:10:39.510 align:middle line:84%
But you started having the odd
one in front of me like this.

00:10:39.510 --> 00:10:40.340 align:middle line:90%
No, help yourself.

00:10:40.340 --> 00:10:40.950 align:middle line:90%
And you're just eating them.

00:10:40.950 --> 00:10:42.500 align:middle line:84%
Just imagine you're
just eating them.

00:10:42.500 --> 00:10:46.070 align:middle line:84%
And then I said to you, oh my,
who gave you those chocolates?

00:10:46.070 --> 00:10:48.410 align:middle line:84%
These were experimental
chocolates,

00:10:48.410 --> 00:10:51.590 align:middle line:84%
they were never
meant to be there.

00:10:51.590 --> 00:10:54.390 align:middle line:84%
Listen, I got a load of
cockroaches, I minced them up.

00:10:54.390 --> 00:10:56.810 align:middle line:84%
I put them in with
a load of glass

00:10:56.810 --> 00:11:00.410 align:middle line:84%
and a half of full of cow's
milk, I did some chemicals,

00:11:00.410 --> 00:11:04.340 align:middle line:84%
I covered them with chocolate
I put them in a box called joy.

00:11:04.340 --> 00:11:06.920 align:middle line:84%
And then what I did is, I cut
some advertising Life Sucks

00:11:06.920 --> 00:11:08.150 align:middle line:90%
Without Joy in it.

00:11:08.150 --> 00:11:09.830 align:middle line:84%
So you were sold on
the whole concept

00:11:09.830 --> 00:11:11.155 align:middle line:90%
of this box of chocolates.

00:11:11.155 --> 00:11:12.530 align:middle line:84%
But I said to you,
fundamentally,

00:11:12.530 --> 00:11:15.020 align:middle line:84%
unfortunately,
there's cockroaches

00:11:15.020 --> 00:11:17.977 align:middle line:84%
is in there because
cockroaches, once ingested,

00:11:17.977 --> 00:11:20.060 align:middle line:84%
gives off a certain chemical
to make you eat more.

00:11:20.060 --> 00:11:21.852 align:middle line:84%
And I am the owner of
the biggest cockroach

00:11:21.852 --> 00:11:23.238 align:middle line:90%
farm in the entire world.

00:11:23.238 --> 00:11:25.280 align:middle line:84%
And it's my interest to
make you eat cockroaches.

00:11:25.280 --> 00:11:26.738 align:middle line:84%
But you won't eat
cockroaches, so I

00:11:26.738 --> 00:11:29.000 align:middle line:84%
have to hide them in amongst
the chocolate in order

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:29.875 align:middle line:90%
for you to have them.

00:11:29.875 --> 00:11:31.610 align:middle line:84%
So sorry, but that's
what they are.

00:11:31.610 --> 00:11:34.340 align:middle line:84%
You ask anybody now if
they have a genuine desire

00:11:34.340 --> 00:11:36.048 align:middle line:84%
to eat that chocolate,
they would say no.

00:11:36.048 --> 00:11:37.548 align:middle line:84%
Now here's the point
I want to make.

00:11:37.548 --> 00:11:39.920 align:middle line:84%
If it's a physical addiction--
this is what people say,

00:11:39.920 --> 00:11:41.290 align:middle line:90%
I couldn't help it!

00:11:41.290 --> 00:11:42.740 align:middle line:84%
Well, then,
therefore, they still

00:11:42.740 --> 00:11:45.080 align:middle line:84%
shouldn't be able to
help it if they went

00:11:45.080 --> 00:11:46.970 align:middle line:90%
for that particular chocolate.

00:11:46.970 --> 00:11:48.838 align:middle line:90%
But if you remove the desire--

00:11:48.838 --> 00:11:50.380 align:middle line:84%
because it is a
point I want to make.

00:11:50.380 --> 00:11:54.080 align:middle line:90%


00:11:54.080 --> 00:11:57.610 align:middle line:90%
Diets require willpower.

00:11:57.610 --> 00:12:01.120 align:middle line:84%
If you successfully want to
change the way you eat forever,

00:12:01.120 --> 00:12:04.310 align:middle line:84%
it does not require willpower,
contrary to popular belief.

00:12:04.310 --> 00:12:07.450 align:middle line:84%
In fact, anything that you
think of that sounds logical

00:12:07.450 --> 00:12:10.930 align:middle line:84%
when it comes to addiction
is the complete opposite.

00:12:10.930 --> 00:12:14.170 align:middle line:84%
For example, if you have
two children in a room,

00:12:14.170 --> 00:12:17.740 align:middle line:84%
one strong-willed and
one is very weak-willed,

00:12:17.740 --> 00:12:19.590 align:middle line:84%
and they both had
a chocolate bar.

00:12:19.590 --> 00:12:22.870 align:middle line:84%
And moreover, they both really
wanted that chocolate bar.

00:12:22.870 --> 00:12:25.630 align:middle line:84%
If you removed the
mass market chocolate

00:12:25.630 --> 00:12:28.625 align:middle line:84%
bar from both of those children
and said, you can't have it,

00:12:28.625 --> 00:12:30.250 align:middle line:84%
who's going to keep
their tantrum going

00:12:30.250 --> 00:12:33.220 align:middle line:84%
for longer at a
greater intensity

00:12:33.220 --> 00:12:35.050 align:middle line:90%
to make sure they get it back?

00:12:35.050 --> 00:12:38.170 align:middle line:84%
Bizarrely, it is the
stronger-willed child.

00:12:38.170 --> 00:12:40.360 align:middle line:84%
The weaker-willed child
will accept the situation

00:12:40.360 --> 00:12:41.560 align:middle line:90%
a lot sooner.

00:12:41.560 --> 00:12:43.480 align:middle line:84%
So why is it, then,
strong-willed people

00:12:43.480 --> 00:12:45.280 align:middle line:90%
have such difficulty on diets?

00:12:45.280 --> 00:12:48.990 align:middle line:84%
It's because, look, if
it's the same two kids,

00:12:48.990 --> 00:12:50.830 align:middle line:84%
there's the chocolate
in the room,

00:12:50.830 --> 00:12:52.150 align:middle line:90%
and they had no desire for it.

00:12:52.150 --> 00:12:53.390 align:middle line:90%
They just didn't want it.

00:12:53.390 --> 00:12:54.765 align:middle line:84%
They had no desire
for it at all.

00:12:54.765 --> 00:12:56.470 align:middle line:90%
And you said, you can't have it.

00:12:56.470 --> 00:12:58.600 align:middle line:84%
They'd look you
and say, OK, fine.

00:12:58.600 --> 00:12:59.920 align:middle line:90%
Don't want it anyway.

00:12:59.920 --> 00:13:02.590 align:middle line:84%
If you took the chocolate
away from them and said,

00:13:02.590 --> 00:13:03.940 align:middle line:90%
you're never having it.

00:13:03.940 --> 00:13:05.980 align:middle line:90%
Who would now be in a tantrum?

00:13:05.980 --> 00:13:07.000 align:middle line:90%
None of them.

00:13:07.000 --> 00:13:07.900 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:13:07.900 --> 00:13:09.640 align:middle line:84%
Because it doesn't
require willpower

00:13:09.640 --> 00:13:11.110 align:middle line:90%
if you have no desire.

00:13:11.110 --> 00:13:15.280 align:middle line:84%
The key is, look, if you remove
the genuine desire for these

00:13:15.280 --> 00:13:19.100 align:middle line:84%
jumped-up, junkie,
sugar-loaded--

00:13:19.100 --> 00:13:23.590 align:middle line:84%
it's not food, for
crying out Bananas.

00:13:23.590 --> 00:13:24.880 align:middle line:90%
If you see it for what it is--

00:13:24.880 --> 00:13:25.910 align:middle line:90%
I was obese.

00:13:25.910 --> 00:13:27.070 align:middle line:90%
I was overweight.

00:13:27.070 --> 00:13:28.600 align:middle line:90%
And I thought this was food.

00:13:28.600 --> 00:13:30.967 align:middle line:84%
In fact, I saw fruits and
vegetables as non-foods.

00:13:30.967 --> 00:13:32.800 align:middle line:84%
I figured you're better
off having a shorter

00:13:32.800 --> 00:13:34.810 align:middle line:90%
life but a much happier one.

00:13:34.810 --> 00:13:36.570 align:middle line:90%
Now I can see it clearly.

00:13:36.570 --> 00:13:37.370 align:middle line:90%
It's a trick.

00:13:37.370 --> 00:13:38.412 align:middle line:90%
It's a very clever trick.

00:13:38.412 --> 00:13:40.360 align:middle line:84%
But once you see,
it becomes easy.

00:13:40.360 --> 00:13:41.495 align:middle line:90%
Diets are hard.

00:13:41.495 --> 00:13:43.370 align:middle line:84%
Because every single
day, you say, I want it,

00:13:43.370 --> 00:13:44.300 align:middle line:90%
but I can't have it.

00:13:44.300 --> 00:13:46.390 align:middle line:84%
And the theory is,
you force yourself

00:13:46.390 --> 00:13:49.630 align:middle line:84%
into a self-imposed
mental tantrum in the hope

00:13:49.630 --> 00:13:52.450 align:middle line:84%
that if you suffer the mental
tantrum for long enough, one

00:13:52.450 --> 00:13:54.220 align:middle line:84%
day, time will
solve the problem,

00:13:54.220 --> 00:13:55.502 align:middle line:90%
time will heal the wound.

00:13:55.502 --> 00:13:56.960 align:middle line:84%
And you'll eventually
reach a stage

00:13:56.960 --> 00:13:58.960 align:middle line:84%
where you can tell the world,
have you heard the news?

00:13:58.960 --> 00:13:59.510 align:middle line:90%
I've done it.

00:13:59.510 --> 00:14:00.310 align:middle line:90%
I've kicked it.

00:14:00.310 --> 00:14:02.450 align:middle line:90%
I'm free of the junk food.

00:14:02.450 --> 00:14:03.910 align:middle line:84%
But when does that
actually happen?

00:14:03.910 --> 00:14:05.193 align:middle line:90%
Two days down the line?

00:14:05.193 --> 00:14:07.360 align:middle line:84%
What are you doing, sitting
around waiting for this?

00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:09.460 align:middle line:84%
People go to sleep to
get rid of the craving.

00:14:09.460 --> 00:14:13.960 align:middle line:84%
If the craving is only in
your mind, 95% of addiction

00:14:13.960 --> 00:14:15.280 align:middle line:90%
is psychological.

00:14:15.280 --> 00:14:16.510 align:middle line:90%
5% is physical.

00:14:16.510 --> 00:14:19.330 align:middle line:84%
Gambling is 100%
psychological and they still

00:14:19.330 --> 00:14:22.690 align:middle line:84%
go through the same
withdrawal process.

00:14:22.690 --> 00:14:24.230 align:middle line:90%
So good and bad news.

00:14:24.230 --> 00:14:28.510 align:middle line:84%
The bad news is, we have the
vast majority of our world

00:14:28.510 --> 00:14:35.700 align:middle line:84%
hooked on sugar-loaded food,
refined fat-loaded food,

00:14:35.700 --> 00:14:38.400 align:middle line:84%
junkie type food that
actually, incidentally,

00:14:38.400 --> 00:14:40.950 align:middle line:84%
they are manipulating in the
way the tobacco companies

00:14:40.950 --> 00:14:43.050 align:middle line:90%
did many, many years ago.

00:14:43.050 --> 00:14:44.590 align:middle line:90%
And we'll find this out.

00:14:44.590 --> 00:14:45.540 align:middle line:90%
We will find this out.

00:14:45.540 --> 00:14:46.740 align:middle line:90%
We're starting to do that now.

00:14:46.740 --> 00:14:48.190 align:middle line:84%
But we will find this
out in the future.

00:14:48.190 --> 00:14:49.320 align:middle line:84%
And they'll look back,
and they'll go, hey,

00:14:49.320 --> 00:14:50.790 align:middle line:90%
I remember hearing that.

00:14:50.790 --> 00:14:53.020 align:middle line:90%
And the same thing is going on.

00:14:53.020 --> 00:14:54.228 align:middle line:90%
That's the bad news.

00:14:54.228 --> 00:14:55.770 align:middle line:84%
We've got obesity
and everything that

00:14:55.770 --> 00:14:58.860 align:middle line:84%
goes along with it,
from type 2 diabetes,

00:14:58.860 --> 00:15:00.450 align:middle line:90%
and so on and so forth.

00:15:00.450 --> 00:15:03.690 align:middle line:84%
The good news is, contrary
to what everybody thinks,

00:15:03.690 --> 00:15:07.433 align:middle line:90%
it's mind-blowingly simple.

00:15:07.433 --> 00:15:08.850 align:middle line:84%
And I know that
I'll get the hairs

00:15:08.850 --> 00:15:10.950 align:middle line:84%
on the back of some
people's necks going up,

00:15:10.950 --> 00:15:14.040 align:middle line:84%
but it's mind-blowingly
simple to remove yourself

00:15:14.040 --> 00:15:15.390 align:middle line:90%
from the diet trap.

00:15:15.390 --> 00:15:16.320 align:middle line:90%
And it is a trap.

00:15:16.320 --> 00:15:17.970 align:middle line:90%
Of course it's a trap.

00:15:17.970 --> 00:15:20.010 align:middle line:84%
Because it goes
against your logic.

00:15:20.010 --> 00:15:21.510 align:middle line:90%
You can't do it.

00:15:21.510 --> 00:15:23.670 align:middle line:84%
I think very few people--
they reckon something

00:15:23.670 --> 00:15:25.830 align:middle line:90%
like 95% of all diets fail.

00:15:25.830 --> 00:15:27.750 align:middle line:90%
That means that 5% succeed.

00:15:27.750 --> 00:15:29.160 align:middle line:90%
5%.

00:15:29.160 --> 00:15:31.200 align:middle line:90%
5%!

00:15:31.200 --> 00:15:32.730 align:middle line:90%
But that's diet mentality.

00:15:32.730 --> 00:15:35.850 align:middle line:84%
You know, 100% succeed
if they're not on a diet,

00:15:35.850 --> 00:15:37.660 align:middle line:84%
they change what
they eat and they see

00:15:37.660 --> 00:15:38.910 align:middle line:90%
the other food for what it is.

00:15:38.910 --> 00:15:40.170 align:middle line:90%
That is true success.

00:15:40.170 --> 00:15:44.800 align:middle line:90%


00:15:44.800 --> 00:15:47.570 align:middle line:84%
The main reason why people come
to me more than anybody else,

00:15:47.570 --> 00:15:50.580 align:middle line:84%
I guess, is because I've studied
addiction more than anything

00:15:50.580 --> 00:15:51.380 align:middle line:90%
else.

00:15:51.380 --> 00:15:53.885 align:middle line:84%
And I'm not part of the
state the obvious brigade.

00:15:53.885 --> 00:15:55.760 align:middle line:84%
And so the idea is, I
don't say-- if somebody

00:15:55.760 --> 00:15:58.220 align:middle line:84%
is overweight, the last
thing they want to hear

00:15:58.220 --> 00:16:00.260 align:middle line:84%
is somebody saying,
by the way, you're

00:16:00.260 --> 00:16:02.450 align:middle line:84%
overweight, as if they
don't know this fact.

00:16:02.450 --> 00:16:04.670 align:middle line:84%
And then, moreover,
you say to them,

00:16:04.670 --> 00:16:06.470 align:middle line:84%
if you ate fruits and
vegetables, cut down

00:16:06.470 --> 00:16:08.270 align:middle line:84%
on the rubbish and
you did more exercise,

00:16:08.270 --> 00:16:09.740 align:middle line:90%
you would be slim and healthy.

00:16:09.740 --> 00:16:12.800 align:middle line:84%
Again, just because somebody
is thick physically,

00:16:12.800 --> 00:16:14.720 align:middle line:84%
it doesn't make
them thick mentally.

00:16:14.720 --> 00:16:16.940 align:middle line:84%
And the more people
realize that these

00:16:16.940 --> 00:16:19.523 align:middle line:84%
are normal human beings that are
simply caught in a trap, then

00:16:19.523 --> 00:16:20.323 align:middle line:90%
the better.

00:16:20.323 --> 00:16:22.370 align:middle line:84%
But of course, most people
come because they're

00:16:22.370 --> 00:16:24.350 align:middle line:84%
suffering either
from excess weight

00:16:24.350 --> 00:16:26.840 align:middle line:90%
or because I had psoriasis.

00:16:26.840 --> 00:16:29.150 align:middle line:84%
So a lot of you think,
well, he managed

00:16:29.150 --> 00:16:32.072 align:middle line:84%
to clear his psoriasis, or
his eczema, or his asthma.

00:16:32.072 --> 00:16:34.280 align:middle line:84%
A lot of these people when
they first come, they say,

00:16:34.280 --> 00:16:37.340 align:middle line:84%
give me a juice to
cure my psoriasis.

00:16:37.340 --> 00:16:39.360 align:middle line:84%
And the human body
doesn't work that way.

00:16:39.360 --> 00:16:43.310 align:middle line:90%
It is holistic, of course

00:16:43.310 --> 00:16:45.460 align:middle line:84%
And you treat all
diseases as one.

00:16:45.460 --> 00:16:46.340 align:middle line:90%
And it is corny.

00:16:46.340 --> 00:16:48.650 align:middle line:84%
And to be honest,
I was so skeptical.

00:16:48.650 --> 00:16:51.058 align:middle line:84%
I would never believed,
and even what I teach.

00:16:51.058 --> 00:16:52.350 align:middle line:90%
I've got to be honest with you.

00:16:52.350 --> 00:16:53.735 align:middle line:90%
I was a science kind of guy.

00:16:53.735 --> 00:16:55.610 align:middle line:84%
I was kind of like,
well, has it been proven?

00:16:55.610 --> 00:16:57.050 align:middle line:90%
Is it logical?

00:16:57.050 --> 00:17:00.110 align:middle line:84%
And I went through God
knows how many doctors.

00:17:00.110 --> 00:17:02.720 align:middle line:84%
I'm not knocking doctors
at all, of course.

00:17:02.720 --> 00:17:05.030 align:middle line:90%
Far from it, in fact.

00:17:05.030 --> 00:17:07.128 align:middle line:90%
They more than have their place.

00:17:07.128 --> 00:17:09.170 align:middle line:84%
But the ones that I had,
and you can't generalize

00:17:09.170 --> 00:17:12.837 align:middle line:84%
by whole industry, they
were part of the state

00:17:12.837 --> 00:17:13.670 align:middle line:90%
the obvious brigade.

00:17:13.670 --> 00:17:14.503 align:middle line:90%
That's all they did.

00:17:14.503 --> 00:17:16.460 align:middle line:84%
They said, Jason, you've
